description.value: This value set includes concepts that represent pregnancy related procedures. This value set is a grouping of two value sets: Procedures During Pregnancy 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.11.1014 with CPT codes and Procedures During Pregnancy 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.11.1015 with SNOMED CT codes. Please see VSAC (https://vsac.nlm.nih.gov) for the latest expansion of these value sets.

purpose.value: The purpose of this value set is to represent types of procedures performed during pregnancy.
